subject: Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Novak Djokovic, the 24-year-old Serbian who is 47-1 this season, beat Jo-Wilfried Tsonga, while Rafael Nadal, the defending champion, ousted Andy Murray.
